title: [Western Harbor, Jetty]
description: Light glitters off of the water on the harbor side of the jetty, its smooth waters a contrast to the rough surf that crashes against the granite blocks on the eastern side.  Wrought iron railings are fused to the sandstone slabs that create a flat walking surface and extend down the length of the jetty as it travels further out into the sea.
